{"tid":1526184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入機場呀!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-01T04:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:13:31.000Z","uid":239679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ebe1bcbe880485f8191a4eef4221ff40bd6dae","tid":1526184,"uid":239679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"呀!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n繼「黑警還眼」後<br />\n901統一口號「黑警恐襲」「黑警放火」<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！"},{"pid":"8337bd777373ebf4c72ec63e7f21ef9f30a3fa5b","tid":1526184,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"c5743bf13ad69a843b05a6bf769c699ba674f853","tid":1526184,"uid":1945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hO54gA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhO54gA1.jpg&h=d74b437d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/738QWA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F738QWA1.jpg&h=514540c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34WZPV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34WZPV2.jpg&h=e88f8e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41gCBA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41gCBA2.jpg&h=ba05256d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f93af7806a3c27a1001717a2753e1a4f01c22974","tid":1526184,"uid":239679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /